Chemistry::File::SMARTS version 0.01
====================================

This object-oriented module is used for reading SMARTS patterns, returning
Chemistry::Pattern objects.

For more information about SMARTS, see the SMARTS Theory Manual at
http://www.daylight.com/dayhtml/doc/theory/theory.smarts.html

This module is under development and doesn't implement the full SMARTS syntax
yet.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:
    - Chemistry::Mol
    - Chemistry::Pattern
    - Text::Balanced
    - Parse::RecDescent


